2011-12-05T19:10:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-05/macpherson-higher-yuan-would-cut-u-s-trade-gap.html
Bloomberg Government analyst Muir 
Macpherson discusses the impact of the Chinese yuan's value on 
the  U.S. trade deficit  with  China  and on U.S. businesses.  Macpherson talks with Bloomberg Government analyst Sanford 
Reback about his study, "A Higher Yuan Would Halve the 
U.S.-China Trade Deficit." (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 10:50
 